# Google Cloud Enterprise Architecture Cheat Sheet (2026)

> **Think Architecture → Then Google Cloud Services**

---

# 1. Architecture Decision Flow

```
Business Objectives
        ↓
Functional Requirements
        ↓
Non-Functional Requirements
        ↓
Constraints
        ↓
Compliance
        ↓
Risks
        ↓
Architecture Pattern
        ↓
Managed Google Cloud Services
        ↓
Production Architecture
```

**Never start with services.**

