# 3. Service Decision Matrix

| Requirement                  | Choose                              |
| ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Central Networking           | Shared VPC                          |
| Connect Two Networks         | VPC Peering                         |
| Expose One Internal Service  | Private Service Connect             |
| Google APIs from Private VM  | Private Google Access               |
| Internet from Private VM     | Cloud NAT                           |
| Google APIs + Internet       | Cloud NAT + Private Google Access   |
| Global Users                 | Global External HTTPS Load Balancer |
| WAF / DDoS                   | Cloud Armor                         |
| Edge Cache                   | Cloud CDN                           |
| Stateless HTTP API           | Cloud Run                           |
| Kubernetes Platform          | GKE                                 |
| GPU / AI Workloads           | GKE                                 |
| PostgreSQL                   | Cloud SQL                           |
| PostgreSQL High Performance  | AlloyDB                             |
| Global SQL                   | Spanner                             |
| Analytics                    | BigQuery                            |
| IoT                          | Bigtable                            |
| Documents                    | Firestore                           |
| Cache                        | Memorystore                         |
| Secrets                      | Secret Manager                      |
| Encryption Keys              | Cloud KMS (CMEK)                    |
| Data Exfiltration Protection | VPC Service Controls                |
| Signed Containers            | Binary Authorization                |
| Migration Assessment         | Migration Center                    |

